    "prompt": "<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure presents a circuit with one battery, one switch, one capacitor, and two resistors. The left vertical side has a battery with e m f epsilon. Moving up the left side and across the top, the circuit splits into two vertical branches. Along the top horizontal side and to the left of the middle vertical branch is a resistor with resistance R sub 1. To the left of that resistor is an open switch S. The middle vertical branch has a capacitor with capacitance C. The right vertical branch has a resistor with resistance R sub 2.\" height=\"109\" src=\"/images/7311c59bad4523fb4da9632b423b73ad.png\" width=\"230\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A circuit contains an ideal battery with potential difference <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"epsilon\"><math alttext=\"epsilon\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>Îµ</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, two resistors with resistances <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 1\"><math alttext=\"R sub 1\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"R sub 2\"><math alttext=\"R sub 2\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>R</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, a capacitor of capacitance <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>C</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, and switch <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"S\"><math alttext=\"S\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>S</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, as shown. The switch is closed. A long time after the switch is closed, the positive plate of the capacitor has charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive Q\"><math alttext=\"positive Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mo>+</mo><mi>Q</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. What change to the circuit can a student make to increase the amount of charge stored on the positive plate of the capacitor?</p>\n",
